Description: Papyrus; Hieroglyphic and Demotic text. This is the Geographical Papyrus, with two fragments of Demotic papyrus, added as patch or protective strip.
Curator's comments: Published in Griffith and Petrie, Two Hieroglyphic Papyri from Tanis (London, 1889). To be published by Jasnow and Ryholt.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (44764) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/44764)
